parameters:
U-um, Lunaroa-san...? I-I'm still... not ready in my
heart...!

We've come this far already. If we don't enjoy ourselves
together, it would be a waste, don't you think?

W-Well, that's true but... I'm a beginner...! I don't know
what to do...! Um...

Haven't you heard anything in the village? Hehe... It's
okay, you don't have to be so scared.

If you're scared... Let's start by inserting it little by
little... from the tip...!

It's okay... Don't be scared... Come on, try inserting a
little more...?
Ah... Somehow, I feel a little... better...\! Maybe...?

That's right... Keep going like that... It feels even better
inside...! Let's try going a little deeper...?

At first, I was scared... but... it's amazing...! Haa...
It's healing...

\SE[15]I'm glad you liked it. \!\SE[1]The thing that
surprised me the most when I left the village was the bath.

\SM[nod]\SE[5]Wow... I wonder how they heat up so much water
like this? \SE[2]Do they have a big bonfire or something?

\SE[0]It's not that we're warming it up. \SE[1]There's a
heat source nearby, and hot boiling water springs up from
it. We cool it down and adjust it to just the right
temperature.

Such... things... \SM[rock]\SE[32] There are so many things
I don't know... outside of the village...\.

\SE\SE[2]Teaching Laura how to take a bath like this was my
secret ambition. \SE[2]...Can I come next to you?
(I was captivated by the wonder of the bath...)

\SE[9] (Ah, ah...? \SE[10] Right now, I'm... \SE[51] Naked
with Luna...? \SE[51] Just the two of us...?)

\SM[jump]\SE[110]Eh. Ah! No... it's nothing...? \SE[8]It's
nothing, but...?

\SE[13]Hmm... why are you turning away? \SE[12]I want to
talk more with Laura...

\SE[8]The area near the water supply is at a temperature
close to the heat source... \SE[7]D-Did you, um, manage to
be okay...?
I-I'm fine...! I was just surprised, that's all...

\SE[38]S-Sorry...? I should have told you properly. Look...
It's not hot... It's not hot... \SE[7]Hug... I'll give you a
hug, okay...
Wow... In Luna's arms... It feels comforting...
\SE[12] (I'm being embraced by Luna while naked...?)

Uh, I'm sorry for interrupting while you're playing the
game...! The girls are about to take a 'break' now...! This
game is a 'preliminary version'. In other words, it's
difficult for me to say, but...

No, I can't show you any more from here! I would be grateful
if you could see it in the 'full version'!

Laura has climbed a little on the Stairway of Adulthood! She
has learned the Sword Technique \i[84] Cheerful Élair!
